&lt;h2 id=&#34;professional-development-and-international-training&#34;&gt;Professional Development and International Training&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Expanding Global Perspectives&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Emphasizing the importance of continuous growth, this short clip captures a glimpse of my two-week intensive training and certification experience in Phoenix, Arizona. Engaging directly in international academic and practical environments continually enriches the EMI methodologies and global perspectives that I bring back to my students in the classroom.&lt;/p&gt;


    
